</P>
<P>
Rebate program -- A June 15 article incorrectly said the city of Oxnard is 
offering rebates to residents who exchange conventional toilets for 
ultra-low-flush models. The rebate program is being considered by the city 
Public Works Department but has not been adopted. 
</P>
</CORRECTION>
